**Structure Reasoning:** Opens with the trend context to give readers immediate orientation (short is rising, not just "one of two options"), then works through each decision factor with summer specificity. The "survival test" section on chlorine/breakage is the most differentiated section vs competitors. Closes with a scannable lifestyle quiz-style decision guide rather than a generic conclusion. Internal link hooks are natural at H2s 4, 6, 7, and 8.

